  <brief_title>Effect of a Low FODMAP Diet in Patients With Ulcerative Colitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Low FODMAP Diet on Gut Microbiota, Inflammation and Gastrointestinal Symptoms in Patients With Ulcerative Colitis in Remission</official_title>
